OL,3,CFans emotional as Scotland kicks off
OL,4,Cfirst World Cup game in 28 years
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAs the game began, many supporters
OL,12,Fwere overcome with emotion as they
OL,13,Fcelebrated the long-awaited return to
OL,14,Fthe global tournament.
OL,16,F"10,224 days since Scotland last
OL,17,Fplayed at a World Cup. Just savour
OL,18,Fthis moment, best national anthem on
OL,19,Fthe planet," one fan posted on X.
