OL,3,CFans emotional as Scotland kicks off
OL,4,Cfirst World Cup game in 28 years
OL,6,F"There are thousands and thousands of
OL,7,FScotland fans who have made the
OL,8,Fjourney and the atmosphere is lively,
OL,9,Fit's positive.
OL,11,F"It's great weather and people are
OL,12,Fhaving a great time and engaging with
OL,13,Fthe local community here in Boston.
OL,14,FEveryone has had such a warm welcome
OL,15,Ffrom the Boston community, so its a
OL,16,Ffantastic situation to be part of."
